WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.500
So I was wondering how closely your team partners with the folks that are in the field, whether it be the stores, the drivers, whoever it might be, to observe some of the creation of your data.

00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:17.799
This is one of the pieces of culture that really excites me about Domino's.

00:00:17.799 --> 00:00:22.200
Everybody that works for Domino's corporate offices knows how to make a pizza.

00:00:22.200 --> 00:00:25.100
So we have a program called Pizza Prep School.

00:00:25.100 --> 00:00:35.599
So when you're onboarded into the company, you participate and we literally have a fully functioning Domino's store in the center of our world headquarters.

00:00:35.599 --> 00:00:40.000
It has glass all around it. You can see it from anywhere in the building.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:46.299
And when you're onboarded, you get with your onboarding group and you run that store for a week.

